    <div class="container">
        <div class="page-header">
            <h1><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Home Affordability Calculator</h1>
            <p>Discover how much house you can truly afford based on your financial situation. Get AI-powered insights for smarter home buying decisions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="calculator-card">
            <div class="calculator-header">
                <h2>Calculate Your Home Affordability</h2>
                <p>Enter your financial details below to see what price range fits your budget</p>
            </div>

            <div class="calculator-form">
                <div class="form-section">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave"></i> Income & Debt Information</h3>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="annualIncome">Annual Income ($)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="annualIncome" placeholder="75,000" min="0">
                            <span class="help-text">Your gross annual income before taxes</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="monthlyDebts">Monthly Debts ($)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="monthlyDebts" placeholder="500" min="0">
                            <span class="help-text">Car loans, credit cards, student loans, etc.</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-section">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-piggy-bank"></i> Down Payment & Savings</h3>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="downPayment">Down Payment Amount ($)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="downPayment" placeholder="20,000" min="0">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="downPaymentPercent">Down Payment Percentage (%)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="downPaymentPercent" placeholder="20" min="0" max="100" step="0.5">
                            <span class="help-text">Typically 3-20% of home price</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-section">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-percentage"></i> Loan Details</h3>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="interestRate">Interest Rate (%)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="interestRate" placeholder="7.5" min="0.1" max="20" step="0.125">
                            <span class="help-text">Current average mortgage rate is 7-8%</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="loanTerm">Loan Term (Years)</label>
                            <select id="loanTerm">
                                <option value="30">30 years</option>
                                <option value="15">15 years</option>
                                <option value="10">10 years</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-section">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Location & Additional Costs</h3>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="state">State</label>
                            <select id="state">
                                <option value="">Select State</option>
                                <option value="CA">California</option>
                                <option value="TX">Texas</option>
                                <option value="FL">Florida</option>
                                <option value="NY">New York</option>
                                <!-- More states would be added in production -->
                            </select>
                            <span class="help-text">For accurate tax estimates</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="propertyTax">Annual Property Tax ($)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="propertyTax" placeholder="Auto-calculated" disabled>
                            <span class="help-text">Estimated based on state</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="homeInsurance">Annual Home Insurance ($)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="homeInsurance" placeholder="1,200" min="0">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="hoaFees">Monthly HOA Fees ($)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="hoaFees" placeholder="0" min="0">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-actions">
                    <button id="calculateBtn" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                        <i class="fas fa-calculator"></i> Calculate Affordability
                    </button>
                    <button id="resetBtn" class="btn btn-outline">
                        <i class="fas fa-redo"></i> Reset
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="results" class="results-container">
                <div class="results-header">
                    <h3>Your Home Affordability Results</h3>
                    <p>Based on your financial information, here's what you can afford</p>
                </div>

                <div class="results-grid">
                    <div class="result-card">
                        <div class="result-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="result-content">
                            <h4>Maximum Home Price</h4>
                            <div class="result-value" id="maxHomePrice">$0</div>
                            <p>Based on your financial profile</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="result-card">
                        <div class="result-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="result-content">
                            <h4>Monthly Mortgage Payment</h4>
                            <div class="result-value" id="monthlyPayment">$0</div>
                            <p>Principal, interest, taxes & insurance</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="result-card">
                        <div class="result-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="result-content">
                            <h4>Loan Amount</h4>
                            <div class="result-value" id="loanAmount">$0</div>
                            <p>After down payment</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="result-card">
                        <div class="result-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-percentage"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="result-content">
                            <h4>Debt-to-Income Ratio</h4>
                            <div class="result-value" id="dtiRatio">0%</div>
                            <p>Lenders prefer under 43%</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="results-breakdown">
                    <h4>Payment Breakdown</h4>
                    <div class="breakdown-grid">
                        <div class="breakdown-item">
                            <span>Principal & Interest</span>
                            <span id="breakdownPI">$0</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="breakdown-item">
                            <span>Property Taxes</span>
                            <span id="breakdownTax">$0</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="breakdown-item">
                            <span>Home Insurance</span>
                            <span id="breakdownInsurance">$0</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="breakdown-item">
                            <span>HOA Fees</span>
                            <span id="breakdownHOA">$0</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="breakdown-item total">
                            <span>Total Monthly Payment</span>
                            <span id="breakdownTotal">$0</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="ai-insights">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-robot"></i> AI-Powered Insights</h4>
                    <div id="aiInsightsText">
                        Enter your financial information above to get personalized insights and recommendations.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="action-buttons">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline">
                        <i class="fas fa-share-alt"></i> Share Results
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn btn-outline">
                        <i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download Report
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn btn-outline">
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email Results
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-sections">
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Understanding Home Affordability</h3>
                <p>Home affordability is determined by several factors including your income, existing debts, down payment amount, credit score, and current mortgage rates. Lenders typically use the 28/36 rule:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>28% Front-End Ratio:</strong> Your monthly housing costs should not exceed 28% of your gross monthly income.</li>
                    <li><strong>36% Back-End Ratio:</strong> Your total monthly debt payments (including housing) should not exceed 36% of your gross monthly income.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Tips to Improve Your Home Affordability</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Increase your down payment savings</li>
                    <li>Pay down existing debts to lower your DTI ratio</li>
                    <li>Improve your credit score for better interest rates</li>
                    <li>Consider less expensive neighborhoods or smaller homes</li>
                    <li>Look into first-time home buyer programs</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

